description: This file initializes and renders the main React application component into the DOM. It imports necessary dependencies including React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the App component, then creates a root and mounts the App within React's strict mode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering a React application into a DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the root.
